# Marketplace assets: the icon ships in the VSIX (referenced from package.json),
# but the hero/feature image and screenshots are served from GitHub raw URLs
# in the README — including them in the VSIX would bloat the package by ~1.3 MB
# without any consumer-visible benefit.
assets/feature.png
assets/screenshots/**
